  <brief_title>Clot Formation and Clot Stability in Patients With Severe Haemophilia A</brief_title>
  <official_title>Clot Formation and Clot Stability in Patients With Severe Haemophilia A - Effect of Recombinant Factor VIII and Tranexamic Acid</official_title>
  <sponsors>
